Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Shinichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a famous high school detective\Nknown throughout the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was forced to take a pill\Nby some organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and became Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter if I'm small!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind's that of a brilliant\N17-year-old detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can solve cases that not\Neven adults can handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Murder Behind the Locked\NDoors of a Celebrity's Apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:56.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 3 days since I shrunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There still hasn't been any\Ninformation about the men in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody would ask\Na detective like him for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,much less give him\Ninformation about those men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko-san, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now,\Nyou're too old to be acting like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set the example for hopeless men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Teitan Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 times 2 is 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 times 3 is 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 times 4 is 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk home together, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must feel kind of lonely since\Nyou just transferred here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we'll be your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, um, I don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying no to Ayumi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violence isn't good, Genta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You got a\Nproblem with me, Mitsuhiko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go, I'm really busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never find those men in black\Nif things keep up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be patient, Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think what would happen\Nif you rushed things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they found out that\Nyou're really Kudo Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would put not just me but all\Nthe people around me in real danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes! Ran-kun came by yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi didn't come\Nto school again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it doesn't look like\Nhe's been home either...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll call the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's just working on\Nanother one of his strange cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He'll be back home\Nsoon enough, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got her convinced for the time being,\Nbut how long can we keep this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made something you'll find\Nuseful for your cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Voice-Altering Bow Tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Voice-Altering"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the dial on the back\Nand you can make all kinds of voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sound like an old man,\Na child, a man, and even a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain it'll come\Nin handy at some point!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that a detective agency\Nwould have much use for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's Conan-kun's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice, we're gonna\Nforce him to be our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mori Detective Agency is closed today.\NIf you've got a job for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...come back... tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god! It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko Okino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! What would a celebrity\Nbe doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I want to hire you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You appear to be troubled, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's spying on you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The furniture's been moved\Nwhenever I come home,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somebody's been sending me\Ncandid photos they took of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I've been getting\Nanonymous phone calls everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If at all possible, we'd like\Nyou to look into it quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Yamagishi, her manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I will investigate\Nas discreetly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need your address\Nand phone number here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you could autograph this too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to write "To Kogoro"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the great detective\NKogoro Mori is on the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to\Nsee a celebrity's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't be getting\Nin the way! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly the kind of place\NI thought Yoko Okino might live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's supposed to know\Nshe lives here, it's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 25th floor, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko-chan in the flesh... Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely have to make\Nfriends with Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he had already been murdered\Nby the time you got back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the person with you\Nat the time was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was I, Kogoro Mori,\NInspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why him, of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember all those cases\Nwe worked on together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And thanks to you,\Nmost of them went unsolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is hot in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always have\Nthe heater on this high?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure I turned\Nit off before I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't the only thing\Nthat's odd, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:08:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very faint, but there are\Ndamp spots all around the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this chair is the only\Nthing still standing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while everything else in the room\Nhas been thrown about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it done to disguise\Nthe time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids shouldn't get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you determined\Nthe cause of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem this knife\Nwas the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that knife belong to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't honestly suspect Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen the victim before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'd have to take a closer look...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you seen him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I guess we haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I saw him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? What did he pick up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strand of hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would her manager\Ntry to hide this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could the murderer have been...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murder took place\Nwhile the door was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the murderer\Nwas the apartment's resident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I could never kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's telling the truth, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because she has\Na key doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't people usually\Nhave a spare key?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Yamagishi-san has my spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi! You're the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko gave you the cold shoulder so\Nyou took it out on him, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Where's the proof\Nthat she didn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a beautiful young woman\Nwould never do anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did have her spare key,\Nbut I lost it 2 or 3 days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not! I was in the dressing room\Nat the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can vouch for him,\Nhe told me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that's what\NYoko-san says, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that we're still\Nlacking something really important
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that could explain everything here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An earring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Inspector, under that sofa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kids stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it, they all ignore me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! This thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just set it to\Nan adult's voice, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, there's something\Nbeneath the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An earring...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yuko-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko Ikezawa-san.\NShe debuted the same time I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that she was upset that Yoko\Ngot her role in a drama series...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer was Yuko Ikezawa!\NArrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to go to the station--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let's have her come here\Nfor questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the inspector! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko Ikezawa did it!\NThere's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the scene of the crime,\Nthe murderer must be Yoko Okino!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The manager's inexplicable action...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the odd marks left\Nbehind in the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pieces are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is how\Nto put them together...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murder took place in Yoko's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one you should suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been here\Nbefore now. I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was this doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I lost that somewhere!\NI'm glad you found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't stop with the earring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The superintendent also said that\Nhe's seen someone who looks like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who looks like me?\NThis is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing your bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never give up, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm the murderer\Njust because of an earring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really busy, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not nearly as busy as little\NMiss Popular Celebrity, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the media gets wind of this,\Nyour image'll take a nosedive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll lose as\Nmuch work as I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you threaten her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They both look exactly\Nthe same from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how did she know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, grownups!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in the way of their\Ninvestigation, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Shinichi were here,\Nhe'd easily solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could that\Nmystery geek have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! He'll be back,\NI'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I have to say\Nfor you to understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you I've\Nnever been here before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty weird lighter, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know this was a lighter\Nif you've never been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Care to explain how you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know someone who has\None just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where does this someone live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been here before,\Nso I don't know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? It's in the hallway...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you knew\Nwhere the bathroom was, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is because you,\NYuko Ikezawa, are the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed that man in this apartment\Nto create a big scandal around Yoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't! I didn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was defend myself\Nwhen he suddenly attacked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit it, I did sneak\Nin here several times
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using the spare key I stole\Nfrom the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to find something,\Nanything that could cause a scandal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I came in this afternoon,\Nthat man suddenly showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I defended myself\Nwith all of my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then escaped\Nas quickly as I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you didn't really kill him\Nin the heat of the moment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I didn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've learned the identity\Nof the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiyoshi Fujie, 22 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon graduating from\NKonan High School,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he began working for\NKakubeni Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konan High School...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your old high school,\NYoko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I know him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't just know him,\Nhe was my high school boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yamagishi-san.\NI can't hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you did this to\Nbreak up with your old flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he was the one\Nwho dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the murderer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko Okino?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko Ikezawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi, the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still missing something\Nwe need to make any deductions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What are we missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dent in the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the room's in shambles,\Nthis chair is the only thing left standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this room's exceptionally\Nhigh temperature...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water splotches\Nleft around the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hair in the corpse's hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-ha! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally solved the puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you, Yamagishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw him as an obstacle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he was capable of starting\Na scandal around Yoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you ran into him\Nwhile he was hiding in here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and proceeded to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi-san isn't the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice nap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're conscious again, Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one left\Nwho could be the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fess up! You'll feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I'll just set\Nit to his voice, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is what I would like to say,\Nbut that isn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really asked me to help you\Nso that I would discover the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would have also prepared something\Nto prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko-san, the same goes for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,especially since the 1st person to suspect\Nwould be the apartment's tenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, then the murderer...\Nis Yuko Ikezawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't do it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she did commit the murder\Nin the heat of the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she wouldn't have told us\Nshe ran into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you're saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, these are only\Neducated guesses at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't hold up as proof that\Nthe three of them are innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is evidence to support it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pretended to slip and then removed\Nstrands of hair from the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! I knew you were the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man was stabbed in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was holding the\Nstabber's hair in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you find that a bit odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one responsible set it\Nall up to look like a murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if he was killed\Nby Yoko-san herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Like a murder"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer is none other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the late Fujie-san himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense! How could he stab\Nhimself in the back with a knife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple trick involving ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He set the heater on high,\Ntook hairs from Yoko-san's brush,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then stood up on a chair\Nand fell back onto a knife
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that was held in place\Nby a block of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find the indentation\Nmark made by the knife's handle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,near where the body was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ice shattered and later melted\Nbecause of the high heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Fujie-san tried\Ntoo hard to frame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Yamagishi-san saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he tried to hide it because he thought\NYoko-san had indeed killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would Fujie-kun\Ndo something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would think that it was\Nbecause he still loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you realize that the two of you\Nlook exactly the same from behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he mistook Yuko-san\Nfor Yoko-san and attacked-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He tried to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not realizing he was talking\Nto Yuko-san and not Yoko-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was completely shocked\Nwhen she resisted him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the feelings of his love being driven\Nto the wall turned into despair and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he dumped me!\NWhy would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not the truth, Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I asked him\Nto break up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found a diary in\Nthe late Fujie-san's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The diary was filled with his pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How even after they broke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was unable to forget about her,\Nso he went to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hoped she would end her career\Nas a celebrity and come back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he wanted to do was clear\Nup the misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last thing he wrote was that\Nhe couldn't live like this any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear this was a tragic story\Nthat consisted of lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,misunderstandings,\Nand coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-kun! You were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed my mind about you,\N"Great Detective"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a little scary, but I've\Nnever been that excited before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think if we make friends\Nwith Conan-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll get to experience lots\Nmore thrills and suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then! We've gotta get\NConan-kun to be our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already back on her feet\Nafter all that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do that. I could never\Nbe as strong as Yoko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even sleep at night\Nwith Shinichi gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:47.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:22:01.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:07.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:17.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:25.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:31.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:41.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:45.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi has been missing\Nfor a week now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:22:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something must have happened to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing like that would\Never happen to Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi... Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Mori Detective--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you might be crying\Nbecause you're worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right. Why would I be crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you right now, Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked to take a sort\Nof dangerous case...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back home once\NI've taken care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I return to my normal body,\NI'll let you hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My real voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My real feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think\Nthese drawings could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet it's a treasure map!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.26,0:24:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for some treasure hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this day forth, we'll be known\Nas the Junior Detective Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use my share of the treasure\Nto eat every gourmet meal in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.35,0:24:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save it, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.01,0:24:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Case of the Coded City Map.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.27,0:24:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.34,0:24:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neon Sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.47,0:25:01.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.37,0:24:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able to crack the code in the next episode?
